.jp/q/CKFH4G6S" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>申请试镜。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000015146.000007006.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">角川株式会社新闻稿</a></p><h2>Hololive Tokoyami Towa x “Polaris Code”合作活动举行</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/f76dbd34d3309e0e0ec35720d3fb8c23-kix.8qbonagposol-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/f76dbd34d3309e0e0ec35720d3fb8c23-kix.8qbonagposol-1024x470.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/f76dbd34d3309e0e0ec35720d3fb8c23-kix.8qbonagposol-1024x470.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/f76dbd34d3309e0e0ec35720d3fb8c23-kix.8qbonagposol-300x138.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/f76dbd34d3309e0e0ec35720d3fb8c23-kix.8qbonagposol-768x353.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/f76dbd34d3309e0e0ec35720d3fb8c23-kix.8qbonagposol-jpg.webp 1200w" width="1024" height="470" /></a></p><p> Hololive<a href="https://twitter.com/tokoyamitowa" target="_blank" rel="noopener">常暗东</a>和与音乐游戏《<a href="https://twitter.com/polarischord573" target="_blank" rel="noopener">北极星密码</a>》的合作活动正在举办。</p><p>期间，游戏中将收录Towa Tokoyami的音乐，您可以在上方的监视器上欣赏音乐视频。另外，常暗东和将作为游戏主角“Contentor”和支持“Contentor”的“Support Snap”登场。</p><p>此外，还可以使用玩“北极星代码”获得的“Mirapo”兑换“常暗东和亚克力立牌”、“常暗东和缶徽章”等。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000350.000053327.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">科乐美娱乐有限公司新闻稿</a></p><h2>虹川拉希七周年纪念现场表演</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/f76dbd34d3309e0e0ec35720d3fb8c23-kix.90argsor2zhv-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/f76dbd34d3309e0e0ec35720d3fb8c23-kix.90argsor2zhv-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/f76dbd34d330